      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "for garnish"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the infused oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add the almond butter and stir until smooth.",
    "Add the noodles and stir to combine with the almond butter mixture.",
    "Cook for 5 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Add the honey, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 2 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Transfer the noodles to a serving dish and garnish with chopped almonds.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
